CRAFTING PATTERN - PREMIUM PDF DOWNLOAD
======================================
Pattern: Cozy Craft Crochet Design
Difficulty: Beginner / Intermediate

ABBREVIATIONS
ch = chain
sc = single crochet
inc = increase (2 sc in one stitch)
dec = decrease (sc 2 together)
sl st = slip stitch
st = stitch

INSTRUCTIONS
============
Row 1: 6 sc in magic ring (6)
Row 2: inc in each st around (12)
Row 3: (sc, inc) around (18)
Row 4-10: sc in each st around (18)
* Stuff firmly with fiberfill.
Row 11: (sc, dec) around (12)
Row 12: dec around (6)
Fasten off and leave a long tail.

